&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://silocitylabs.com/uploads/2018/02/Core51822-size.jpg&#34;&gt;2mm pitch headers, ugh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://silocitylabs.com/uploads/2018/02/Core51822-size.jpg&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

